These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, lawyer
1. the lawyer is on the far left or far right##3
2. the journalist is on the right of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Job   | lawyer | journalist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, bus
1. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Transport   | car | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
2 different games are played: bridge, chess
1. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
2. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Game   | chess | bridge |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, argentine
1. the argentine is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the chinese is on the left or right of the argentine##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Nationality   | argentine | chinese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-5::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, ritmeester
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |     2     |
| Cigar   | vegafina | ritmeester |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-6::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, epic
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
2. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | disaster |

